          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-[var(--color-slate)] leading-relaxed">
            <p>ICF stands for Insulated Concrete Forms. The "forms" are interlocking foam blocks that hold their shape while concrete is poured inside. Unlike traditional plywood forms that get stripped away, ICF forms stay permanently as built-in insulation.</p>
