          <div class="mt-4 text-[var(--color-slate)] leading-relaxed">
            <p>For walls only, ICF runs 5-10% higher than wood frame construction. For a complete home including all components, expect 8-12% more than comparable wood-frame construction. The premium varies based on project complexity, size, and location. ICF basements typically add $15,000-$30,000 compared to a poured foundation with future finishing.</p>
