            <p>Yes, and it's easier than finishing a traditional concrete basement. ICF walls have plastic web strips embedded in the foam - you screw drywall directly to these without framing or adding insulation. The walls are already insulated, flat, and ready for finishing. Handy homeowners often tackle this themselves.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-[var(--color-cream)] p-6">
