            <p>ICF excels in cold climates. The continuous insulation envelope and concrete's thermal mass keep indoor temperatures stable even during Ontario's -20C winters. ICF homes require smaller heating systems and run them less often. The thermal mass also prevents temperature swings during spring and fall shoulder seasons when heating and cooling needs fluctuate.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

